data.description: This charming home offers a great chance for first-time purchasers or for investors wishing to boost their income with a little TLC. There is a sizable walk-in closet in the primary bedroom of this home. The huge dining area with built-in cabinets (pantries), as well as a utility closet with washer and dryer hookups, are located next to the kitchen, which has concrete counter tops. The remodeled bathroom is equipped with custom shower head and faucets.  Enjoy entertaining your visitors in the large backyard, featuring a chicken coop and three storage structures. Even parking for your boat or RV is available!
